title: 4 bedroom, 1 bath, 4-car heated garage, A/C, Deck
posting_body: ['4 bedroom (3 up, 1 down), 1 ceramic bath, Rambler style built in 1968 (but has since been updated), 2,000 s.f. total up & down, finished, carpeted basement.', 'The home has a insulated and heated, double wide - double deep, 4-car garage that totals just under 1,000 s.f. in size.', 'This home is in a Great Location, just one block from the bus line and near Spring Lake Park High School.', 'Conveniently located between Central and University Ave, About 1 mile from Northtown Mall.', "The home is also located near Mercy Hospital Unity Campus and has many businesses and restaurants located near by, such as Sam's club, Walmart, Cub, Walgreens, Outback, Red Lobster, etc...", 'The home has a west facing living room with large windows, carpeting and vertical blinds.', 'Two of the bedrooms have hardwood floors and two have ceiling fans.', "It also has all gas appliances, a built-in dishwasher, under sink filtered water, water softener, newer 95% high efficiency house furnace and extra insulation in the attic for lower energy bills, vinyl windows, patio door leading to a 17' x 17' deck partially shaded by a beautiful red maple tree.", 'If you choose to use it, the home has a built-in Alarm System that is centrally monitored for an extra fee.', 'The are beautiful, mature maple trees for awesome shade.', 'Also, an automatic yard sprinkler system, cedar yard planter boxes and a spot for a garden, if you like to grow your own veggies or flowers.', 'This home is located in a quiet, friendly neighborhood with wonderful long-term neighbors.', "In the garage there is an 80,000 BTU Modine hanging furnace with thermostat in the detached, insulated garage with garage door opener, Front and rear of garage can be separated by the internal 16' overhead garage door.", 'Both garage areas have plenty of lighting and outlets.', 'There is also a side overhead garage door that opens to the back yard.', "You'll also have a built-in work bench and cabinets for nice storage space.", 'There is a pull down stairway in garage rafters for storage of light items only.', 'For added convenience and security there are multiple motion detector lights.', 'The home is available for Oct 1st, could be available for occupancy as early as September 1st.', 'No Section 8 No Pets, No Smoking.', 'Tenant pays all utilities.', 'Rent is $2,195 per month, plus deposit']
